title: Fluid NFL Situations This Summer
itunes:title: Fluid NFL Situations This Summer
description:
PRIDE EPISODE! A bar filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal, Colleen Wolfe, and Ricky Hollywood bring you an episode filled with love. It's Pride month so the gang wanted to be together. We talk Aaron Rodgers and MVP seasons and also bachelorette parties and things that make us happy. Colleen's dad, Ed Wolfe, takes us in for a landing.
